"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?37/9/38034?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Colectomy (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?10/39/10869?source=see_link\">",
